Insider Activity


Individual




Mark W. Albers



Mr. Mark W. Albers is Senior Vice President at Exxon Mobil Corp., a Member at Society of Petroleum Engineers, Inc., a Member at The Institution of Engineers Australia, and a Member at CEO Forum. He is on the Board of Directors at United States Council for International Business and The National Action Council for Minorities in Engineering.
Mr. Albers was previously employed as President by ExxonMobil Development Co., Operations Manager by Esso Australia Pty Ltd., and a Trustee by Museum of Fine Arts of Houston.
He received his undergraduate degree from Texas A&M University.



